  "contentHtml": "<h2>Chris Dalla Riva + Alan Paul Talk</h2>\n<p><span>Yesterday, I had the pleasure of speaking with </span><span><a href=\"https://open.substack.com/users/20224-alan-paul?utm_source=mentions\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Alan Paul</a></span><span> about my book </span><em><a href=\"https://bio.site/uncharted_territory\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Uncharted Territory: What Numbers Tell Us about the Biggest Hit Songs and Ourselves</a></em><span>. It was an incredible discussion because Alan is one of the best music writers out there. </span></p>\n<p><span>Along with his biography on Stevie Ray Vaughn, he is one of the leading authorities on the Allman Brothers Band. You should check out </span><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/stores/author/B001KI072W\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">his books</a><span> and his newsletter, </span><em><a href=\"https://alanpaul.substack.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Low Down and Dirty</a></em><span>.</span></p>\n<h4>Discussion about this video</h4>\n<img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!IN68!,w_150,h_150,c_fill,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep,g_auto/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-video.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fvideo_upload%2Fpost%2F169706514%2F6ffc5895-cd73-425d-a544-a547e77fd570%2Ftranscoded-00001.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n<img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!V-mE!,w_150,h_150,c_fill,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep,g_center/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd9d219ec-1f5c-429a-afd0-a649d3ad39f8_1024x724.webp\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n<img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!63sP!,w_150,h_150,c_fill,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep,g_center/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4fedc2d5-bcda-48eb-8c17-6d3c0ed6de11_1200x800.webp\" width=\"150\" 